---
// No props needed for this component
---

<section
  class="min-h-screen flex items-center relative overflow-hidden bg-background"
>
  <!-- Background Elements -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 overflow-hidden pointer-events-none">
    <!-- Grid -->
    <div
      class="absolute inset-0 bg-[linear-gradient(to_right,theme(colors.blue.900/50)_1px,transparent_1px),linear-gradient(to_bottom,theme(colors.blue.900/50)_1px,transparent_1px)] bg-[size:3.5rem_3.5rem] opacity-30"
    ></div>
    
    <!-- Blurry Gradient Shapes -->
    <div class="absolute -top-1/4 -left-1/4 w-1/2 h-1/2 bg-secondary/20 rounded-full filter blur-3xl opacity-40"></div>
    <div class="absolute -bottom-1/4 -right-1/4 w-2/3 h-2/3 bg-accent/20 rounded-full filter blur-3xl opacity-30"></div>
    <div class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-1/3 h-1/3 bg-primary/10 rounded-full filter blur-3xl opacity-50"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="container mx-auto px-6 relative z-10 pt-20">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
      <div class="text-right">
        <div class="inline-block mb-6" data-aos="fade-down">
          <div
            class="flex items-center gap-2 text-primary/90 bg-blue-900/30 rounded-full py-2 px-4 border border-blue-500/50 backdrop-blur-sm"
          >
            <span class="text-xs font-medium">نرحب بأفكاركم المبتكرة</span>
            <div
              class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-primary animate-pulse"
            ></div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <h1 class="text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold mb-6 text-white" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">
          نحوّل أفكارك إلى
          <span
            class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-400 to-cyan-400"
            >منتجات رقمية متميزة</span
          >
        </h1>

        <div class="space-y-6 text-sm text-gray-300 mb-8" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="200">
          <p class="leading-relaxed">
            في YAS، لا ننتظر أن تصلنا الأفكار مكتملة؛ بل نأخذ رؤية العميل
            وفكرته، ونحوّلها بخبراتنا التقنية والإبداعية إلى منتج رقمي
            فعّال، متكامل، وجاهز للنمو — حتى وإن كانت في صورتها الأولية، أو
            مجرد حاجة في السوق.
          </p>
          <p class="leading-relaxed font-medium text-blue-400">
            نجاح العميل هو نجاحنا؛ لذا لا نكتفي بالتنفيذ فقط، بل نشاركه في بناء
            النجاح.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 justify-start" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="300">
          <a
            href="#services"
            class="group relative inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-3 font-medium text-white transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out rounded-full overflow-hidden hover:scale-105 text-sm bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-500 to-blue-600 shadow-lg shadow-blue-500/20 hover:shadow-blue-500/40"
          >
            <div class="relative flex items-center gap-2">
              استكشف خدماتنا
              <i
                class="ri-arrow-left-line opacity-70 group-hover:-translate-x-1 transition-transform"
              ></i>
            </div>
          </a>
          <a
            href="#contact-section"
            class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-white/80 hover:text-primary transition-colors group text-sm"
          >
            <span>تواصل معنا</span>
            <i
              class="ri-arrow-left-line group-hover:-translate-x-1 transition-transform"
            ></i>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Animated Elements -->
      <div class="relative hidden lg:block" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="400">
        <div class="relative rounded-full p-8">
          <!-- Floating Elements -->
          <div
            class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-20 h-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-500/20 to-transparent rounded-full animate-float"
            style="animation-delay: 0s"
          ></div>
          <div
            class="absolute top-1/4 right-0 w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-cyan-400/20 to-transparent rounded-full animate-float"
            style="animation-delay: 0.5s"
          ></div>
          <div
            class="absolute bottom-0 left-1/4 w-24 h-24 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-600/20 to-transparent rounded-full animate-float"
            style="animation-delay: 1s"
          ></div>

          <!-- Tech Pattern -->
          <div
            class="relative w-full aspect-square rounded-full border-2 border-blue-800/50 p-8 backdrop-blur-sm"
          >
            <div
              class="absolute inset-0 bg-[linear-gradient(to_right,theme(colors.blue.900/50)_1px,transparent_1px),linear-gradient(to_bottom,theme(colors.blue.900/50)_1px,transparent_1px)] bg-[size:2rem_2rem] rounded-full"
            ></div>
            <div
              class="h-full rounded-full border-2 border-blue-700/60 flex items-center justify-center"
            >
              <img src="/assets/yass logo-05.png" alt="YAS Logo" class="h-full w-full object-contain p-8 opacity-90" />
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section> 